Join authors and abortion doulas Carly Kol and Emulsify for an engaging event centered on _Let’s Talk About Abortion_—a compassionate, age-appropriate guide to discussing abortion care with children. Through a live reading, Q&A, and access to Plan C materials, attendees will gain tools to foster open, empathetic conversations about reproductive health with the young people in their lives.